Details

This attack deals damage using the Inverse Battle type chart. In most cases, that means it deals super-effective damage against Electric, Grass, Ground and Dragon type Pokémon, and deals not-very-effective damage against Water and Flying type Pokémon.

An even number of instances of the Inverse Battle effect results in normal type advantages. For example, a grounded attacker that uses Negative Energy during Eerie Terrain will attack with non-inverted Electric type effectiveness.
